		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite: Proficiency in &amp;reference[athletics].</strong></em></p><p><em>You are skilled at restraining creatures with your bare hands.</em></p><ul><li><p>You can use a @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-rules.JournalEntry.eS0uzU55fprQJqIt.JournalEntryPage.zaI1nuc41wANKoFX]{grapple} check on a creature you are already grappling in place of an attack. If you succeed, the creature is &amp;reference[restrained]. This does not require another empty hand. You cannot restrain a creature more than one size larger than you.</p></li><li><p>When you are &amp;reference[grappled], you can choose to automatically grapple the creature that grappled you if you have an empty hand to do so.</p></li><li><p>You can move at full speed while grappling a creature of your size or smaller, pulling any grappled creature(s) with you.</p></li></ul>",
